  <div id="text-content_6fbab453-22f4-4b9e-a0fe-0d471cde886f" class="text-block-content">
    <p>In Course Navigation, click the <strong>Grades</strong> link.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="open_assignment" data-step-uuid="23707727-49b4-4ce3-9d33-442186c186d3">
    <h2 id="open_assignment" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Open Assignment Menu</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/004/795/863/original/08d24a6f-6157-422a-a281-0b65e8ba6a06.png" srcset="" alt="Open Assignment" height="233" width="614">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_06c97a33-c05d-4a09-851c-a39cdf6add6f" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Any assignment with hidden grades is indicated by the <strong>Visibility</strong> icon [1].</p>
<p>Hover over the assignment column header and click the<strong> Options</strong> icon [2].</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="curve_grades" data-step-uuid="240f7069-dbc8-4bce-b612-11c07aec2836">
