        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/004/795/865/original/f78f9b60-fe5f-449d-9141-6b9eede9d46a.png" srcset="" alt="Open Post Grades Tray" height="399" width="615">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_2303e13c-fde7-41b5-9e82-201eb5cd622b" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Click the <strong>Post grades</strong> link.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
        <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-2" id="view-all-grades-posted" data-step-uuid="bda2a394-6cb9-45b5-b563-7eaf9cd59518">
    <h3 id="view-all-grades-posted" class="step-title screensteps-heading">View Other Messages</h3>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/003/305/672/original/8f30c511-eec6-4702-b3d0-3e224aeec0fb.png" srcset="" alt="View Other Messages" height="400" width="590">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_d70ae66e-febb-4a3c-a693-518eeaeb0550" class="text-block-content">
    <p>If student grades are already posted, the Options menu displays that all grades are posted [1]. To <a href="/t5/Instructor-Guide/How-do-I-hide-grades-that-were-previously-posted-in-the/ta-p/721" target="_blank">hide student grades</a>, click the <strong>Hide grades</strong> link [2].</p>
<p>If there are no grades or comments on the assignment, the Options menu will display that there are no grades to hide or post [3].</p>
